reviewText: The item arrived on time and in perfect condition, well packed and protected, but unfortunately, the article does not match the one shown in the picture.

The DVD 1 and the CD contain the same set list, the DVD contains some video paper clips and videoes in concert.
 The DVD 2 contine documentaries and interviews it brings over of Rage.
 The presentation is of luxury since the discs come contained in a metal box of collection close to a leaflet.
 Actually it is one good piesa for a collector.
